resources.string: The technical extravaganza of GRIET , Pragnya is back!! Pragnya is a national level technical symposium,organised by IEEE Student Branch in Gokaraju Rangaraju Institute of Engineering and Technology to be held on 16th,17th and 18th of October ,2014.It conducts workshops that educate the students on the latest and upcoming technologies.Also a wide range of technical and non-technical events are held that challenge the minds of students all over the country to prove their expertise.
